===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} ''[[Graecia]]'' < [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[Γραικός]]''' (''Graekos''), a character in Greek mythology, the son of [[w:Thessalos|Thessalos]], the king of [[w:Fthia|Fthia]], whom '''[[Ἑλλάς]]''' (''[[Hellas]]'', "Greece") and '''[[Ἕλληνες]]''' (''[[Hellene]]s'', "the Greeks") were also named after.

